   <text:p text:style-name="Fără_20_spațiere"><text:span text:style-name="T4"><text:s/></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T3"><text:tab/>218 ŞT. OLTEANU, Meşteşugurile, p. 48; Istoria oraşului Bucureşti, I, p. 74.</text:span></text:p>
