   <text:p text:style-name="P3"><text:span text:style-name="T8"><text:s/></text:span><text:tab/>3« Ibidem, p. 284 (nr. CCXXIX).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P3"><text:span text:style-name="T8"><text:s/></text:span><text:tab/>317 Ibidem.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Fără_20_spațiere"><text:span text:style-name="T4"><text:s/></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T3"><text:tab/> M DRH, B, I, p. 330 (nr. 205).</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P3"><text:span text:style-name="T8"><text:s/></text:span><text:tab/>319 Nu e treGUt în documente anterior lui 1500.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P3"><text:span text:style-name="T8"><text:s/></text:span><text:tab/>320 DRH, B, I, p. 291 (nr. 179).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P3"><text:span text:style-name="T8"><text:s/></text:span><text:tab/>321 Ibidem, p. 465 (nr. 285).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Fără_20_spațiere"><text:span text:style-name="T4"><text:s/></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T3"><text:tab/>322 Ibidem, p. 185 (nr. 105). Orientativ, numai ca o indicaţie generală, a se vedea harta dată de I. CORFUS, Agricultura Ţării Româneşti în prima jumătate a secolului al XlX-lea, Bucureşti, 1969, p. 402.</text:span></text:p>
